<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <title>Use cases - ghostanalytics</title>
    <meta name="description" content="How different teams put ghostanalytics to work: SaaS, ecommerce, agencies, publishers, and developers. The same cookieless script, from a solo blog to a funded product.">
    <meta name="theme-color" content="#0a0c0e">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Geist:wght@400;500;600;700;800&family=Geist+Mono:wght@400;500;600&display=swap">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/marketing.css">
  </head>
  <body>
    @include('site-nav')

    <main>
      <nav class="shell subnav" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
        <a href="/">Home</a><span class="sep">/</span>
        <span>Use cases</span>
      </nav>

      <section class="feat-hero shell">
        <span class="kicker">Use cases</span>
        <h1>Real numbers for teams that respect their visitors.</h1>
        <p>The same cookieless script fits a solo blog or a funded SaaS. Here is how different teams put ghostanalytics to work, and which features carry the weight.</p>
        <div class="hero-actions">
          <a class="btn primary" href="/#install">Get your script tag</a>
          <a class="btn ghost" href="/dashboard">See a live dashboard</a>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="reveal section shell" aria-label="Use cases">
        <div class="usecases">

          <a class="usecase" href="/use-cases/saas" data-no-router>
            <svg class="usecase-viz" viewBox="0 0 480 168" preserveAspectRatio="xMidYMid meet" role="img" aria-label="A signup funnel narrowing from 8,420 visitors to 289 activated users" style="display:block;width:100%;height:168px;background:#101317">
              <rect x="6" y="6" width="468" height="156" rx="10" fill="#15191e" stroke="rgba(233,238,240,0.09)"></rect>
              <text x="26" y="34" fill="#6d777c" font-family="'Geist Mono',ui-monospace,monospace" font-size="11" letter-spacing="1.2">SIGNUP FUNNEL</text>
              <rect x="54" y="52" width="372" height="26" rx="6" fill="#46d3c0" fill-opacity="0.92"></rect>
              <rect x="110" y="90" width="260" height="26" rx="6" fill="#46d3c0" fill-opacity="0.58"></rect>
              <rect x="165" y="128" width="150" height="26" rx="6" fill="#46d3c0" fill-opacity="0.36"></rect>
              <text x="240" y="70" text-anchor="middle" fill="#04201c" font-family="'Geist',sans-serif" font-size="13" font-weight="600">8,420 visitors</text>
              <text x="240" y="108" text-anchor="middle" fill="#04201c" font-family="'Geist',sans-serif" font-size="13" font-weight="600">612 signups</text>
              <text x="240" y="146" text-anchor="middle" fill="#eef2f3" font-family="'Geist',sans-serif" font-size="13" font-weight="600">289 activated</text>
            </svg>
            <div class="usecase-body">
              <h3>SaaS</h3>
              <p>Follow visitors from landing page to signup and activation, and attribute each account to the channel that earned it. No consent banner between a first-time visitor and your call to action.</p>
              <span class="textlink">Analytics for SaaS</span>
            </div>
          </a>

          <a class="usecase" href="/use-cases/ecommerce" data-no-router>
            <svg class="usecase-viz" viewBox="0 0 480 168" preserveAspectRatio="xMidYMid meet" role="img" aria-label="Revenue trending upward over the last 30 days" style="display:block;width:100%;height:168px;background:#101317">
              <rect x="6" y="6" width="468" height="156" rx="10" fill="#15191e" stroke="rgba(233,238,240,0.09)"></rect>
              <text x="26" y="34" fill="#6d777c" font-family="'Geist Mono',ui-monospace,monospace" font-size="11" letter-spacing="1.2">REVENUE · LAST 30 DAYS</text>
              <path d="M40,146 L40,112 L92,120 L144,96 L196,104 L248,78 L300,86 L352,60 L404,68 L448,44 L448,146 Z" fill="#46d3c0" fill-opacity="0.13"></path>
              <polyline points="40,112 92,120 144,96 196,104 248,78 300,86 352,60 404,68 448,44" fill="none" stroke="#46d3c0" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></polyline>
              <circle cx="448" cy="44" r="4.5" fill="#46d3c0"></circle>
              <text x="26" y="58" fill="#eef2f3" font-family="'Geist',sans-serif" font-size="20" font-weight="700" letter-spacing="-0.5">$65.7k</text>
            </svg>
            <div class="usecase-body">
              <h3>Ecommerce</h3>
              <p>Tie carts, checkouts, and revenue back to the campaigns that drove them, with numbers that match your store. Your customer data never flows into an ad graph you do not control.</p>
              <span class="textlink">Analytics for ecommerce</span>
            </div>
          </a>

          <a class="usecase" href="/use-cases/agencies" data-no-router>
            <svg class="usecase-viz" viewBox="0 0 480 168" preserveAspectRatio="xMidYMid meet" role="img" aria-label="Three client sites, each with its own visitor trend" style="display:block;width:100%;height:168px;background:#101317">
              <rect x="6" y="6" width="468" height="156" rx="10" fill="#15191e" stroke="rgba(233,238,240,0.09)"></rect>
              <text x="26" y="34" fill="#6d777c" font-family="'Geist Mono',ui-monospace,monospace" font-size="11" letter-spacing="1.2">CLIENT SITES</text>
              <g>
                <rect x="26" y="48" width="136" height="104" rx="8" fill="#101317" stroke="rgba(233,238,240,0.09)"></rect>
                <text x="40" y="70" fill="#9aa4a9" font-family="'Geist Mono',monospace" font-size="9.5">northwind.co</text>
                <polyline points="40,132 62,120 84,124 106,104 128,110 148,88" fill="none" stroke="#46d3c0" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></polyline>
                <text x="40" y="94" fill="#eef2f3" font-family="'Geist',sans-serif" font-size="13" font-weight="600">12,480</text>
              </g>
              <g>
                <rect x="172" y="48" width="136" height="104" rx="8" fill="#101317" stroke="rgba(233,238,240,0.09)"></rect>
                <text x="186" y="70" fill="#9aa4a9" font-family="'Geist Mono',monospace" font-size="9.5">lumen-studio</text>
                <polyline points="186,128 208,118 230,122 252,112 274,116 294,100" fill="none" stroke="#46d3c0" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></polyline>
                <text x="186" y="94" fill="#eef2f3" font-family="'Geist',sans-serif" font-size="13" font-weight="600">7,920</text>
              </g>
              <g>
                <rect x="318" y="48" width="136" height="104" rx="8" fill="#101317" stroke="rgba(233,238,240,0.09)"></rect>
                <text x="332" y="70" fill="#9aa4a9" font-family="'Geist Mono',monospace" font-size="9.5">harbor-goods</text>
                <polyline points="332,126 354,128 376,118 398,120 420,112 440,116" fill="none" stroke="#46d3c0" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></polyline>
                <text x="332" y="94" fill="#eef2f3" font-family="'Geist',sans-serif" font-size="13" font-weight="600">5,140</text>
              </g>
            </svg>
            <div class="usecase-body">
              <h3>Agencies</h3>
              <p>Run every client site from one login and share a clean, read-only report in a single link. Exact data that stays in your own database, free of the sampling that makes agency reports hard to defend.</p>
              <span class="textlink">Analytics for agencies</span>
            </div>
          </a>

          <a class="usecase" href="/use-cases/publishers" data-no-router>
            <svg class="usecase-viz" viewBox="0 0 480 168" preserveAspectRatio="xMidYMid meet" role="img" aria-label="Top articles ranked by readers over the last 30 days" style="display:block;width:100%;height:168px;background:#101317">
              <rect x="6" y="6" width="468" height="156" rx="10" fill="#15191e" stroke="rgba(233,238,240,0.09)"></rect>
              <text x="26" y="34" fill="#6d777c" font-family="'Geist Mono',ui-monospace,monospace" font-size="11" letter-spacing="1.2">TOP ARTICLES · 30 DAYS</text>
              <g font-family="'Geist Mono',monospace" font-size="10" fill="#9aa4a9">
                <text x="26" y="59">Against cookie banners</text>
                <rect x="26" y="66" width="428" height="10" rx="5" fill="rgba(233,238,240,0.07)"></rect>
                <rect x="26" y="66" width="428" height="10" rx="5" fill="#46d3c0" fill-opacity="0.92"></rect>
                <text x="26" y="95">Cutting page weight in half</text>
                <rect x="26" y="102" width="428" height="10" rx="5" fill="rgba(233,238,240,0.07)"></rect>
                <rect x="26" y="102" width="262" height="10" rx="5" fill="#46d3c0" fill-opacity="0.66"></rect>
                <text x="26" y="131">A field guide to referrers</text>
                <rect x="26" y="138" width="428" height="10" rx="5" fill="rgba(233,238,240,0.07)"></rect>
                <rect x="26" y="138" width="184" height="10" rx="5" fill="#46d3c0" fill-opacity="0.44"></rect>
              </g>
            </svg>
            <div class="usecase-body">
              <h3>Publishers &amp; blogs</h3>
              <p>See which posts hold attention and where a spike came from, counted exactly rather than sampled. Core Web Vitals sit beside each article, so a slow page never quietly loses its audience.</p>
              <span class="textlink">Analytics for publishers</span>
            </div>
          </a>

          <a class="usecase" href="/use-cases/developers" data-no-router>
            <svg class="usecase-viz" viewBox="0 0 480 168" preserveAspectRatio="xMidYMid meet" role="img" aria-label="A live stream of custom events arriving in real time" style="display:block;width:100%;height:168px;background:#101317">
              <rect x="6" y="6" width="468" height="156" rx="10" fill="#15191e" stroke="rgba(233,238,240,0.09)"></rect>
              <text x="26" y="34" fill="#6d777c" font-family="'Geist Mono',ui-monospace,monospace" font-size="11" letter-spacing="1.2">CUSTOM EVENTS</text>
              <circle cx="410" cy="30" r="4" fill="#46d3c0"></circle>
              <text x="422" y="34" fill="#46d3c0" font-family="'Geist Mono',monospace" font-size="11" letter-spacing="0.5">LIVE</text>
              <polyline points="30,120 74,124 118,100 162,108 206,82 250,92 294,66 338,76 382,52 426,60 452,42" fill="none" stroke="#46d3c0" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></polyline>
              <circle cx="118" cy="100" r="3" fill="#46d3c0"></circle>
              <circle cx="206" cy="82" r="3" fill="#46d3c0"></circle>
              <circle cx="294" cy="66" r="3" fill="#46d3c0"></circle>
              <circle cx="382" cy="52" r="3" fill="#46d3c0"></circle>
              <circle cx="452" cy="42" r="5" fill="#46d3c0"></circle>
              <text x="30" y="150" fill="#9aa4a9" font-family="'Geist Mono',monospace" font-size="10.5">ghost('plan_upgraded', { to: 'pro' })</text>
            </svg>
            <div class="usecase-body">
              <h3>Developers</h3>
              <p>A one-line script, a one-function events API, and a clean HTTP endpoint to read it all back. Self-hostable, PostgreSQL-backed, and privacy-first by default. Your data stays yours.</p>
              <span class="textlink">Analytics for developers</span>
            </div>
          </a>

        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="reveal section shell" aria-label="Get started">
        <div class="cta-band">
          <h2>Your numbers. Your visitors' privacy. Both intact.</h2>
          <div class="cta-actions">
            <a class="btn primary" href="/#install">Get your script tag</a>
            <a class="btn ghost" href="/dashboard">See a live dashboard</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>

    @include('site-footer')
  </body>
</html>
